{"tid":139700,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"求救，爸爸捭人屈，希望各位巴絲幫幫手","createTime":"2017-03-01T15:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T08:45:48.000Z","uid":75199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52f786e391e5246b768c7458d2a500efb26ccee9","tid":139700,"uid":75199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事發係琴日下午1330左右（2017-2-28日）<br />\n地點係上海街豉油街(電單車標位對出）<br />\n<br />\n是咁的......<br />\n揸客貨van Ge 爸爸係上海街豉油街比個電單車司機屈，話爸爸部車撞到佢，佢地首先係口角， 但爸爸要趕住車野捭人，就唔同佢嘈， 扭車走。爸爸一扭車，個電單車司機就大叫，你唔好走丫！ 你撞到我丫，之後就扮野訓低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/01/230902_755bc38bc98cb8e367b5bf74d9d490ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F01%2F230902_755bc38bc98cb8e367b5bf74d9d490ec.jpg&h=56a36719&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就係圖中位置 ， 而圖中見到果部電單車就正正係果部電單車ge位置，爸爸部車就係佢後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問各位巴絲 ， 有冇人見到或者咁岩經過，或有車cam 影到，可唔可以通知我，我好唔甘心爸爸捭人屈。<br />\n<br />\n跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"accf81b6d17a92b540c83430b1acfb7e25efa140","tid":139700,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:25:26.000Z","msg":"呢個年代仲有人唔裝車cam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd28d8f094be2bf9ae004daf9ddc082f1f8cff83","tid":139700,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0